subject: Bobsledding
Skeleton (Sport)
World Cup (Skiing)
lead_paragraph: A United States team including the Olympic 100-meter hurdler Lolo Jones won a gold medal in the combined bobsled-skeleton event at the world championships in St. Moritz, Switzerland.
